br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LD7dnxE.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知道點解今次中共病毒疫情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共派政黨</span></span></strong>，特別係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>，民意得分直線上升???<br />\n答案：係因為支那01係背後緊搞鬼！！<br />\n『<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200428-chi&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=80ea3250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi</a><br />\n，[/size=3][/i]而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯則顯著上升8.4分。</span></span>』<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWHAT THE FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年反送中大家唔係未領教過 唔記得嘅幫你重溫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那01滲透連登亂鳩咁帶風向 搞到我哋抗爭路途艱難咗咁多 你唔係唔記得呀嘛？<br />\n2019.10.06 曲解個別人士看法 為連登仔「主流」意見<br />\n不排除發表裝修過火言論人士係01自己友裡應外合<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3372054/org/275d81f556563cc11f7f4df5bd1b3a68.jpg/ZNGnljnlcF3bfZKzYGOuq1MS4Xzj4awRMtY9gTLWPYE?v=w1920r16_9\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01"},{"pid":"df8a7a401f5260f295921a862583bc7a0e41039c","tid":1992531,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T20:02:31.000Z","msg":"輸民意......了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863bdd32e8f91c32284fabdc059873cef79b93a3","tid":1992531,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T21:47:20.000Z","msg":"因為omdb 隨住時間流逝愈顯得佢係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/